Name: Don't Crash - The Political Game
About the game: WARNING THIS GAME CRASHES WHEN YOU DIE! IT'S THE POINT OF THE GAME! DISCLAIMER: Don't Crash - The Political Game. DOES NOT CONDONE OR SUPPORT ANY TYPE OF REAL WORLD VIOLENCE OR HATE TOWARD ANY GROUP OF ANY KIND! Key Features: 1. Game Quits on Death 2. Sprite Ai 3. First Person Shooting 4. Four Weapons With More To Come 5. Political Humor 6. Consistent Updates With New Content 7. Consistent Bug Patches Game includes features like shooting Trump 3d Sprites. FPS shooting, various guns, and avoiding possible traps. As well as some political humor along the way. This game is a work in progress. There are 3 levels and more to be added in the future. I'm a solo Dev and I like it that way!
